(734, 112, 'description', '<span style="color: #4e505f;">Choose your preference of our standard or Large Studio Apartments.  These have the same facilities although the Large Studio Apartment is more spacious and generally has a separate kitchen, whilst the standard Studio Apartment has a kitchenette incorporated in the lounge and dining area.  Apartments have a double or king size bed and are rear-facing, with the exception of the small number of apartments on the Lower Ground Floor.  A small number of Large Studio Apartments have the option of inter-connecting with a similar number of One Bedroom Apartments to make a really spacious combination. </span>'),
