(809, 128, 'description', '<span style="color: #4e505f;">With only 5 Two Bedroom Apartments in the building, these are one of our most sought after apartment types.  Always side facing (overlooking Gloucester Road) these apartments normally have a king size bed in the master bedroom and twin beds in the second bedroom.  In some cases, the twin beds can alternatively be configured as a second king size.  There are two bathrooms – on en suite to the master bedroom and one of the hallway of the apartment.  Excellent value for a family or two couples travelling together, these apartments can fit an extra rollaway bed, when needed, to accommodate a fifth guest.</span>'),
