(312, 1, '2014-06-25 14:50:02', '2014-06-25 14:50:02', '<p style="color: #4e505f;">Enjoy a lower rate with our Special Offer Discount when staying 5 nights or longer without losing the flexibility to change dates or even cancel, if you need to do so.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Take the opportunity of the lower rate with Special Offer Discount to spoil yourself with a larger apartment, which are even better value.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Terms of Special Offer Discount:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: #4e505f;">\r\n	<li>Special Offer Discount on a stay of 5 nights or longer.</li>\r\n	<li>Stay at any time from now up to November 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Credit or debit card details are required only to guarantee your reservation.</li>\r\n	<li>Payment on arrival at The Harrington.</li>\r\n	<li>Cancel without charge up to 48 hours prior to arrival.</li>\r\n	<li>Change the dates of stay without penalty.</li>\r\n	<li>Special Offer Discount is strictly subject to availability.</li>\r\n	<li>We reserve the right to change or remove Special Offers at any time without prior notice. In the event of such a change, existing reservations will be honoured.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Location:</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">The Harrington – 1 Harrington Gardens is handily located 2 minutes’ walk from Gloucester Road tube station, with many shops, supermarkets and restaurants in the immediate vicinity.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Exclusive shopping in London’s Knightsbridge or High Street Kensington is a short tube ride or a 10 minute walk.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">Many of London’s main museums are close by and Oxford Street, Regent Street and Westfield London are a short tube ride away.  The Harrington is also very conveniently placed for events at London’s Earl’s Court and Olympia.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #4e505f;">A large number of <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="London events" href="http://www.theharrington.com/time-out/" target="_blank">events</a> take place in London throughout the year.  So, start planning your visit to London now and don’t forget to book your apartment securely at <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000;" title="1 Harrington Gardens" href="http://www.theharrington.com/v4/props/1-harrington-gardens/">The Harrington web site</a>, taking advantage of our Special Offer Discount.</p>', 'Special Offer Discount – 5 Nights And Longer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '221-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-25 14:50:02', '2014-06-25 14:50:02', '', 221, 'http://localhost/v2.theharrington.com/221-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
